              "id": "rq1",
              "name": "research_query",
              "value": "=Research for a {{ $('get_genre_config').first().json.genre_name || $('get_genre_config').first().json[0]?.genre_name }} short story about: {{ $('workflow_trigger').item.json.premise }}. Provide factual details about: {{ $('workflow_trigger').item.json.research_topics || $('workflow_trigger').item.json.premise }}. Include scientific accuracy, historical details, cultural context, and sensory details useful for fiction writing.",
