    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const research = $('research_topic').first().json.message || '';\nconst style = $('style_analysis').first().json.output || $('style_analysis').first().json.text || '';\nconst trigger = $('workflow_trigger').first().json;\nconst genre = $('get_genre_config').first().json;\nconst genreData = Array.isArray(genre) ? genre[0] : genre;\nconst genreName = genreData?.genre_name || 'Science Fiction';\nconst guidelines = genreData?.writing_guidelines || '';\nconst length = parseInt(trigger.length) || 3000;\n\nconst prompt = `You are a world-class science fiction author.\n\n## Genre\n${genreName}\n\n## Genre Guidelines\n${guidelines}\n\n## Research\n${research}\n\n## Writing Style\n${style}\n\n## Assignment\nWrite a complete short story of approximately ${length} words.\n\n- Premise: ${trigger.premise}\n- Tone: ${trigger.tone}\n- Target length: ${length} words\n\n## Structure\nWrite the story with natural scene breaks (use --- between scenes). Include:\n1. Opening: Establish the world, introduce the protagonist\n2. Rising action: Develop conflict, deepen character\n3. Climax and resolution\n\nWrite the story text directly. No JSON wrapping, no metadata, no scene labels. Just the story.`;\n\nreturn [{ json: { prompt: prompt, title: trigger.premise?.split(' ').slice(0, 5).join(' ') || 'Untitled' } }];"
      },
